description._content: Description: See Governor's 520 of 20th June 17. Location: Borneo Date: 20 June 0017 ------------------------------------------------------ Description: Constabulary defending stockade. Spectacular operation. Location: Borneo Date: 24 August 1918 ------------------------------------------------------ Description: Constabulary falling back.
